===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  mb_regex_encoding(?string $encoding = null): string|bool~

Set/Get character encoding for a multibyte regex.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{encoding}

  The {encoding} parameter is the character encoding. If it is omitted or null,
  the internal character encoding value will be used.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

If {encoding} is set, then Returns true on success or false on failure. In this
case, the internal character encoding is NOT changed. If {encoding} is omitted,
then the current character encoding name for a multibyte regex is returned.

===============================================================================
